Spreadsheet: Scenario: <em>Two famous archaeologists have discovered a series of underground passageways leading to an ancient civilization. The duo packed their bags full of necessary supplies, turned on their headlights, and crawled into the hole that led to an underground structure.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>The duo tie a rope and climb down.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Before proceeding, Aisha rubs their hand along the ground to check for traps.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Aisha triggers a pressure plate. A hidden passage leading forward opens up in front of her.
Spreadsheet: NeutralFeedback: Aisha finds no traps so she decides it is safe to continue forward.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Aisha touches the ground triggering a pressure plate. This releases a boulder which falls grazing her shoulder dealing damage.

Spreadsheet: EncounterIntro: <em>The duo continues into a dark and narrow underground cave.
Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Becky turns on their flashlight to illuminate the way forward.
Spreadsheet: RewardFeedback: Becky’s light illuminates a gemstone vein along the cavern wall. She chips off and adds a few gemstones to their pack.
Spreadsheet: NeutralFeedback: Becky uses the light to make it easier for her to continue forward with no issues.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: The light disturbs a flock of bats, which fly past Becky causing her to drop several rations from their pack.

Spreadsheet: PlayerAction: Aisha decides to jump over it.

Spreadsheet: NeutralFeedback: Aisha makes it over and she continues on.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Aisha slips and falls into the puddle. She gets bit by numerous leeches dealing damage.

Spreadsheet: NeutralFeedback: Becky realizes that she may need to fight the skeletons.

Spreadsheet: NeutralFeedback: Aisha finds no traps so she decides it is safe to continue forward.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Aisha touches the ground triggering a pressure plate. This releases a boulder which falls grazing her shoulder dealing damage.

Spreadsheet: NeutralFeedback: Aisha finds no traps so she decides it is safe to continue forward.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Aisha touches the ground triggering a pressure plate. This releases a boulder which falls grazing her shoulder dealing damage.

Spreadsheet: NeutralFeedback: Aisha finds no traps so she decides it is safe to continue forward.
Spreadsheet: PunishFeedback: Aisha touches the ground triggering a pressure plate. This releases a boulder which falls grazing her shoulder dealing damage.
